      <title>Hindalco花费52亿美元扩展到新业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/hindalco-to-spend-5-2-billion-to-expand-into-new-businesses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度的Aditya Birla集团计划在其铝，铜和专业氧化铝业务上投资4,500亿卢比（52亿美元），因为单元Hindalco Industries Ltd.试图扩展到高级工程和上游运营。]]></description>
